{"tid":2208989,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家買股票前要諗止蝕（2）","createTime":"2020-09-19T10:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T20:23:22.000Z","uid":311141,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e4bfe5203bfc96a1a4f4c9f5b9887e173ba60a","tid":2208989,"uid":311141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"估唔到我第一個post 推爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家買股票前要諗止蝕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gbjxgT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gbjxgT</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家支持同bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢排都有留意個市，但都冇入返啲股票喇，主要short qqq 等待股市平靜返，但大家既回覆我都有盡量睇<br />\n<br />\n總括來講，大部分人認為如果係好既股票，應該strong hold 到末日，跌=係時候大平賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，例如呢排tesla 表現，非常亮眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，止蝕既人全部做左傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差既股票，就應該止蝕<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得如果要分辨好股票，就要做好多事前準備同正確研究基本面同未來分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，先可以確定係好野<br />\n相反，如果無深入研究或者自己研究方向錯咗，我地就可能以為係好股票，但其實隻股票無想像咁好<br />\n<br />\n同埋都好睇你投資長線定係短線，我自己就睇短至中線，只有少少時間做股票研究（本身有正職），同埋唔肯定研究方向係唔係正確，所以當我見到隻股票唔係按我計劃發展，我就會止蝕離場<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家各有各理由止蝕或strong hold，只係想同新手講，因為你經驗尚淺，未必㨂得啱好既股票，及早止蝕風險會低於strong hold <br />\n<br />\n相反，如果你係老手，分析㨂股從不出錯，同埋睇長線，就應strong hold 到尾，跌就溝，當然唔需要止蝕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為你唔會㨂中垃圾股<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好拗喇，兩邊都啱<br />\n個市短期跌 - 止蝕啱，strong hold 都無錯，因為睇長線<br />\n個市長遠升 - strong hold 啱，止蝕都無錯，因為睇短線<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家齊齊賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衷心多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9377a42dc0141dc247798c2b9e5ae9dd71098dc5","tid":2208989,"uid":240250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"柒左就潛啦，仲開個新post出黎比人屌"},{"pid":"e2bab614b67d0337c9cd9a9168c432bd1674677e","tid":2208989,"uid":364041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"止蝕師係有料"},{"pid":"fb1e117d7aca9f54b4585752c9d906d79d9509e3","tid":2208989,"uid":311141,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9377a42dc0141dc247798c2b9e5ae9dd71098dc5","tid":2208989,"uid":240250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"柒左就潛啦，仲開個新post出黎比人屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"哇 原來係駡戰狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4g29A16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g29A16.png&h=497c9498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我早就係紅圈個位走哂貨再 short QQQ，已經賺返哂<br />\n<br />\n柒頭你呢？高位接貨呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係度吠吠吠，你呢啲人就最廢<br />\n講野無內容，又係度吋柒柒"},{"pid":"946f6c5881ef4a49735e566bffd7ce42bc13d5a4","tid":2208989,"uid":328625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370accf0765d9b918472b13e5d3e8b212b520ed6","tid":2208989,"uid":299433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb1e117d7aca9f54b4585752c9d906d79d9509e3","tid":2208989,"uid":311141,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9377a42dc0141dc247798c2b9e5ae9dd71098dc5","tid":2208989,"uid":240250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"柒左就潛啦，仲開個新post出黎比人屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"哇 原來係駡戰狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4g29A16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g29A16.png&h=497c9498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我早就係紅圈個位走哂貨再 short QQQ，已經賺返哂<br />\n<br 